oji\" /> <br />\n搵廁所仲要搵乾淨既<br />\n有條毛黑蚊蚊果啲真係坐唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"so true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每去一個地方都祈求嗰度個廁所係乾淨+有消毒液<br />\n如果出便痾咗，一返屋企就要即刻沖涼洗屎忽<br />\n<br />\n其實而家出親街都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4fabb87d37ff16952fb027481e0bf52c19b17e","tid":928444,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"一樣 IBS 已經5年都係咁 放棄左醫<br />\n好彩返工唔算遠 就算食左早餐痾完返工途中都會想肚痾<br />\n最好解決都係唔食早餐 買支寶礦力算尻數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93592f2db7272bccb531ca21526ea26eb613e062","tid":928444,"uid":44966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"不嬲都易肚瀉 食完就急 都慣咗<br />\n呢個月唔知咩事<br />\n有日痛到爭d暈<br />\n坐又痛企又痛瞓又痛<br />\n<br />\n之後睇完西醫好似好d<br />\n跟住又嚟料持續右下腹奄奄痛<br />\n食乜屙返乜出嚟唔消化<br />\n成日屙水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba560368eb688d69097fa9b11635650852511af8","tid":928444,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738d7dcf3ce26b50021dd43ed167f11915220878","tid":928444,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44a3677aea2cf3ad66522f94e870a1219a04ffa","tid":928444,"uid":8773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25ef5a6778884552d396ce5302a0b1c43b94da8","tid":928444,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"朝朝返工準時肚痛要痾<br />\n仲要一痾就一定遲到嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n另外，一緊張就黎料<br />\n食野污糟少少又黎料<br />\n<br />\n成日搵廁所好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"一撚樣<img src=\